    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei aeterni. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king #Imperial/royal_diploma #Camera_regis"
                            ref="#people/21">Berengarius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs>. Noverit omnium fidelium sanctae Dei
                        Aecclesiae nostrorumque presentium scilicet ac futurorum industria, eo quod
                        <persName key="#Count #Offersio/donatio #Imperial/royal_diploma" ref="#people/166"
                            >Anselmus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs>
                        <placeName key="#City_territory"><geogName>Veronensis</geogName></placeName> per <rs
                            key="#Offersio/donatio">cartulam oblationis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Camera_of_other_public_authorities"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/47">Beati Silvestri</orgName> sito <placeName
                            ref="#places/">Nonantulas</placeName> contulerit pro remedio animae
                        nostrae et suae <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs> quae dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Allocation_to_churches"><geogName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#estates/">Duas Robores</geogName></placeName> et predia
                        quaedam locata in <rs key="#Ports">portu</rs> et <rs key="#Fundi">fundo</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Ports #Churches #Fundi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Allocation_to_churches"><geogName
                            key="#Ports #Churches #Fundi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Allocation_to_churches">Rovescello</geogName></placeName> una
                        cum <rs key="#Churches">capella</rs> ibidem in honore <orgName
                            key="#Churches #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Allocation_to_churches">sancti Zenonis</orgName> edificata <rs
                            key="#City_territory">finibus</rs> Veronensium sub integritate, sic ut
                        nos dudum nostrae largitatis precepto eidem Anselmo comiti iure proprietario
                        concessimus, ac per hoc duo prefati monasterii venerabiles <rs key="#Monks"
                            >monachi</rs>, <persName key="#Priests #Monks"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>
                        videlicet <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> et <persName key="#Deacons #Monks"><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs>, per <persName key="#Intercessory #fidelisOf" ref="#people/21">Odelricum</persName> nostrum
                        karissimum <rs key="#fidelisOf">fidelem</rs> et nobilem virum suppliciter
                        nobis innuerunt <rs key="#Intercessory">petentes</rs> nostrae pietatis
                        clementiam, ut eandem cartulam oblationis simul cum prefata curte Duas
                        Robores et predia sita Rovescello pariter cum iam dicta capella ad honorem
                        beati Zenonis constructa in integrum, sicut nos hactenus pretaxato Anselmo
                        comiti per nostrum donavimus <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma"
                            >preceptum</rs>, ita divino amore succensi nostrae confirmationis titulo
                        corroborare dignaremur. Quorum precibus acclinati, eandem curtem Duas
                        Robores cum omnibus appenditiis suis, casis videlicet, terris, vineis,
                        campis, pratis, pascuis, silvis, salectis, sationibus, aquis aquarumque
                        decursibus, molendinis, piscationibus, districtionibus, simul cum prediis et
                        capella in Rovescello adiacentibus, cum <rs key="#Teloneum">theloneis</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Tolls">ripaticis</rs> et <rs key="#Angaria">publicis
                            vectigalibus</rs> in integrum, prout nos prefato Anselmo comiti
                        contulimus <rs key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">proprietario iure</rs> et
                        idem Anselmus per suae oblationis cartulam predicto monasterio contulit, per
                        hoc nostrum regale preceptum confirmamus eidem monasterio usque im perpetuum
                        ad habendum et commutandum, quatenus abbas eiusdem monasterii qui in tempore
                        prefuerit ita licenter omnia superius comprehensa teneat, vindicet tamquam
                        alia iura sui monasterii, totius potestatis contradictione et inquietudine
                        remota. Si quis igitur hoc nostrae confirmationis preceptum infringere vel
                        violare temptaverit, sciat se compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri optimi
                            libras centum</rs>, medietatem <rs key="#Camera_regis">camerae
                            nostrae</rs> et <rs key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem
                            prefato monasterio Sancti Silvestri eiusque rectoribus</rs>. Quod ut
                        verius credatur et diligentius observetur, manu propria roborantes de anulo
                        nostro subter insigniti iussimus Signum domni Berengarii serenissimi regis.
                            <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> iussu regio recognovi et subscripsi. Data
                        .v. kal. novemb., anno dominicae incarnationis .dccccxi., domni vero
                        Berengarii serenissimi regis xxiiii. indictione .xv. Actum
                            <placeName>Papie</placeName>. in Christi nomine feliciter, amen. </ab>
                </div>
